---
source: crates/claim/src/claimfile.rs
expression: render(&full_draft())
---
---
id: payments/libfoo-pin
checks:
  - kind: cmd
    run: "grep -q 'libfoo==4.2' requirements.txt"
    negate: true
    when: every 30d
max-age: 120d
supports:
  - "requirements.txt#libfoo"
  - other-claim
---
We pin libfoo at 4.2.
